{"tid":1926487,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"睇完立場情人節個訪問有感而發，寫咗首歌俾手足","createTime":"2020-03-15T07:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T07:37:07.000Z","uid":353184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef017c43e4a62c1e7e72e35178c9f673b57289d2","tid":1926487,"uid":353184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VnMNw_ZMG-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVnMNw_ZMG-A&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOydjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=ecd34ade\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VnMNw_ZMG-A</a><br />\n<br />\n2020年2月14日立場新聞出了一篇報導，訪問一個17歲少女，她男朋友10月時在運動中被捕，正在還柙。那個少女每週都會山長水遠走到懲教所探望男友，情人節當然也不例外，即使每次只能見15分鐘。我看完報導後，想起應該有不少抗爭者也有同樣遭遇吧？想為他們寫一首歌，希望他們可以盡快和親愛的人團聚。<br />\n<br />\n（報導：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n_uoWELuRLQ）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn_uoWELuRLQ%EF%BC%89&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOydjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=f9b6867a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n_uoWELuRLQ）</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFeel free to CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"aeb4fda51808947337b0610aecc40639f61b8d80","tid":1926487,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"最後又搵個差佬埋單"},{"pid":"0ef783cbf86040694321ca4a194f58a7623ca2b0","tid":1926487,"uid":353184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aeb4fda51808947337b0610aecc40639f61b8d80","tid":1926487,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"最後又搵個差佬埋單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:09:47.000Z","msg":"唔會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3193a78aacb7bef07a3b7f26a06563c1f4c91a","tid":1926487,"uid":353184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15